'''艾薇儿·丹妮卡·海恩斯'''{{efn|或译'''埃夫丽尔·海恩斯'''<ref>{{cite web | url = http://m.cankaoxiaoxi.com/ym/20201125/2425485.shtml | title = 11月25日译名发布：Avril Haines | website = 参考消息 | date = 2020-11-25 | accessdate = 2020-12-06 }}</ref>。}}（{{lang-en|Avril Danica Haines}}，{{bd|1969年|8月29日||}}），是一名[[美国|美国]]律师，現任美國[[國家情報總監|國家情報總監]]。曾于[[巴拉克·奥巴马|巴拉克·奥巴马]]政府担任[[美国副国家安全顾问|副国家安全顾问]]，也是首位女性[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]{{tsl|en|Deputy Director of the Central Intelligence Agency|中央情报局副局长|副局長}}。加入中情局前，海恩斯曾是{{tsl|en|Office of White House Counsel|白宫律师办公室}}国家安全事务主席副律师。

2020年11月23日，海恩斯获[[美国总统|美国总统]]当选人[[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]提名为國家情報總監，成为首位出任该职务的女性。2021年1月正式就任，海恩斯成为[[乔·拜登内阁|拜登內閣]]裡第一个被[[美国参议院|參議院]]通过的内阁成员<ref>{{Cite news|title=Avril Haines Becomes First Woman Director of National Intelligence|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/avril-haines-becomes-first-woman-director-of-national-intelligence-11611187964|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2021-01-21|accessdate=2021-01-21|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Dustin|last=Volz}}</ref>。

== 早年 ==
海恩斯1969年8月29日在纽约曼哈顿出生<ref name ="Klaidman13">{{cite magazine | url =http://mag.newsweek.com/2013/06/26/avril-haines-the-least-likely-spy.html | title =The Least Likely Spy | first =Daniel | last =Klaidman | magazine =Newsweek | date =2013-06-26 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160119111534/http://www.newsweek.com/2013/06/26/avril-haines-least-likely-spy-237616.html | archive-date =2016-01-19 | dead-url =yes | access-date =2013-11-29 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=PqadDwAAQBAJ&q=%22The+same+year+I+got+my+PHD,+Adzie+had%22&pg=PT152|title = A Curious Life: From Rebel Orphan to Innovative Scientist|isbn = 9781642931945|last1 = Haines|first1 = Thomas H.|last2 = Lewis|first2 = Mindy|date = 2019-08-06|access-date = 2020-12-06|archive-date = 2020-12-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201206164441/https://books.google.com/books?id=PqadDwAAQBAJ&q=%22The+same+year+I+got+my+PHD%2C+Adzie+had%22&pg=PT152|dead-url = no}}</ref>。母亲阿德丽安·拉平（Adrian Rappin）是画家，曾患[[慢性阻塞性肺病|慢性阻塞性肺病]]，后因感染禽[[结核病|结核病]]，于海恩斯15岁时离世。父亲{{tsl|en|Thomas H. Haines|托马斯·海恩斯}}是生物学家、[[纽约市立学院|纽约市立学院]]名誉教授，曾创办{{tsl|en|CUNY School of Medicine|纽约市立学院医学院}}，任生物化学系系主任<ref>{{cite news
 | url=http://observer.com/2008/07/serious-chemistry/
 | title=Serious Chemistry
 | first=Dana
 | last=Rubinstein
 | newspaper=The New York Observer
 | date=2008-07-15
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014060258/http://observer.com/2008/07/serious-chemistry/
 | archive-date=2016-10-14
 | dead-url=no
 | accessdate=2020-12-06
 }}</ref>。

从{{tsl|en|Hunter College High School|亨特学院高中}}毕业后，海恩斯前往日本游学一年，其间加入[[东京|东京]]精英[[柔道|柔道]]馆[[講道館|講道館]]<ref name="Klaidman13" />。1988年就读[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]，主修[[理论物理学|理论物理学]]，在校期间曾在[[海德公园_(芝加哥)|海德公园]]的汽修店兼职修汽车引擎<ref name="Klaidman13" />。1991年到[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]学习驾驶飞机，结识后后来的丈夫大卫·达维吉（David Davighi）。1992年凭[[文学士|文学士]]学位毕业<ref>{{cite web | url =http://mag.uchicago.edu/university-news/notes-4%20 | title =The University of Chicago Magazine | first =Katherine | last =Muhlenkamp | publisher =University of Chicago Press | location =Chicago, Illinois | year =2013 | archive-url =https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmagazine-dev.uchicago.edu%2Funiversity-news%2Fnotes-4%2520&date=2017-02-03 | archive-date =2017-02-03 | dead-url =yes | access-date =2013-11-29 }}</ref>。

1992年，海恩斯搬到[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[巴尔的摩|巴尔的摩]]，就读于[[约翰斯·霍普金斯大学|约翰斯·霍普金斯大学]][[哲学博士|哲学系]]。不过她一年或辍学，与后来的丈夫在拍卖会上买下巴尔的摩{{tsl|en|Fell's Point, Baltimore|坠落点 (巴尔的摩)|坠落点}}的一家酒吧，这家酒吧之前在缉毒行动中被查封<ref name="Klaidman13" />。两人将这间酒吧改造成独立书店，兼作咖啡馆<ref name="BS01">{{cite news | url = http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1994-01-09/features/1994009208_1_bookstore-cafe-world-cafe-vegetarian-cafe | title = Food and coffee, with books, billiards and student chefs | first = Mary | last = Corey | newspaper = The Baltimore Sun | date = 1994-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161220192119/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1994-01-09/features/1994009208_1_bookstore-cafe-world-cafe-vegetarian-cafe | archive-date = 2016-12-20 | dead-url = no | accessdate = 2020-12-06 }}</ref>。为纪念亡母，海恩斯为这家店取名阿德丽安咖啡书店（Adrian's Book Cafe），还把阿德丽安的写实油画挂满店铺<ref name="BS01" />。1997年，书店获《{{tsl|en|Baltimore City Paper|巴尔的摩城市报}}》“最佳独立书店”称号，卖点是非主流的藏书、在地作家、[[情色|情色]]作品朗诵夜及小型出版社作品<ref>{{cite news | url = http://blogs.citypaper.com/index.php/the-news-hole/new-cia-number-two-was-once-a-fells-point-fixture/ | title = New CIA number two was once a Fells Point fixture | first = Evan | last = Serpick | date = 2013-06-13 | access-date = 2014-02-09 | newspaper = City Paper | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221191832/http://blogs.citypaper.com/index.php/the-news-hole/new-cia-number-two-was-once-a-fells-point-fixture/ | archive-date = 2014-02-21 }}</ref>。书店举办各类朗诵会，其中的情色作品朗诵会在海恩斯获奥巴马总统任命为中情局副局长时受到媒体关注<ref name=MediaMatters>{{cite news |url=https://www.mediamatters.org/hillary-clinton/erotica-high-heels-and-handbags-how-beltway-press-should-cover-powerful-women |title=Erotica, High Heels, and Handbags: Is This How The Beltway Press Should Cover Powerful Women? |publisher=Media Matters |first=Eric |last=Boehlert |date=2013-06-14 |archive-date=2016-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220131218/http://mediamatters.org/print/blog/2013/06/14/erotica-high-heels-and-handbags-is-this-how-the/194471 |access-date=2017-02-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1995-05-22/features/1995142103_1_romp-haines-fells | title = Between The Covers Erotica Nights A Hot Item At Fells Point Bookstore | first = Mary | last = Corey | newspaper = The Baltimore Sun | date = 1995-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170118132410/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1995-05-22/features/1995142103_1_romp-haines-fells | archive-date = 2017-01-18 | dead-url = no | accessdate = 2020-12-06 }}</ref>。海恩斯还出任坠落点企业协会主席，直到1998年<ref>{{cite news | url =http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1998-01-04/news/1998004073_1_fells-point-benefits-district-additional-tax | title =Fells Point debates tax to add desired services Benefits: Homeowners and merchants want a safer, cleaner neighborhood. But some residents don't think they can afford a community district levy. | first =Brenda J. | last =Buote | newspaper =The Baltimore Sun | date =1998-01-04 | archive-date =2016-03-04 | dead-url =no | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065930/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1998-01-04/news/1998004073_1_fells-point-benefits-district-additional-tax | accessdate =2020-12-06 }}</ref>。

1998年，海恩斯就读[[乔治城大学法律中心|乔治城大学法律中心]]，2001年获[[法律博士|法律博士]]学位<ref>{{cite news | url =https://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/reliable-source/wp/2013/06/13/avril-haines-new-cia-2-ran-indie-bookstore-remembered-for-90s-erotica-nights/ | title =Avril Haines, new CIA #2, ran indie bookstore remembered for '90s 'erotica nights' | first1 =Roxanne | last1 =Roberts | first2 =Emily | last2 =Yahr | newspaper =The Washington Post | date =2013-06-13 | archive-date =2016-03-05 | dead-url =no | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160305045313/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/reliable-source/wp/2013/06/13/avril-haines-new-cia-2-ran-indie-bookstore-remembered-for-90s-erotica-nights/ | accessdate =2020-12-06 }}</ref>。

== 生涯 ==

=== 公职生涯早期 ===
[[File:Susan_E._Rice,_Avril_Haines_and_Lisa_Monaco.jpg|thumb]]（左）、艾薇儿·海恩斯和{{tsl|en|Lisa Monaco|丽莎·摩纳哥}}（右），2015年]]
2001年，海恩斯担任[[海牙国际私法会议|海牙国际私法会议]]法务官<ref>{{cite journal | url = http://cjicl.org.uk/2013/04/23/international-law-a-mans-world-2/ | title = International Law: A Man's World? | first = Naomi | last = Burke | journal = Cambridge Journal of International and Comparative Law | publisher = Cambridge University | location = Cambridge, England | date = 2013-04-23 | archive-date = 2016-03-27 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160327031228/http://cjicl.org.uk/2013/04/23/international-law-a-mans-world-2/ | access-date = 2013-11-29 }}</ref>。2002年出任[[美国联邦第六巡回上诉法院|美国联邦第六巡回上诉法院]]法官{{tsl|en|Danny Julian Boggs|丹尼·朱利安·博格斯}}的书记员<ref>{{cite web | url =http://blogs.mcclatchydc.com/washington/2013/06/changes-at-the-cia-.html | title =Changes at the CIA | first =Lesley | last =Clark | agency =McClatchy News Service | website =mcclatchydc.com | date =2013-06-12 | access-date =2013-11-29 | archive-date =2013-12-03 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20131203035747/http://blogs.mcclatchydc.com/washington/2013/06/changes-at-the-cia-.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

2003年至2006年供职于{{tsl|en|Legal Adviser of the Department of State|美国国务院法律顾问|国务院法律顾问}}办公室，先是在贸易事务办公室工作，后转到政治军事事务办公室<ref name="WHOPS">{{cite web | url =http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2013/04/17/president-obama-announces-more-key-administration-posts | title =President Obama Announces More Key Administration Posts | author =White House Office of the Press Secretary | publisher =whitehouse.gov | date =2013-04-17 | access-date =2013-06-22 | archive-date =2013-06-16 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130616100314/http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2013/04/17/president-obama-announces-more-key-administration-posts | dead-url =no }}</ref>。2007年至2008年担任[[美国参议院外交委员会|美国参议院外交委员会]]多数党（民主党）的副首席法律顾问，时任民主党主席为乔·拜登<ref>{{cite web | url =https://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2013/06/12/191061035/cia-deputy-director-michael-morell-retires | title =CIA Deputy Director Michael Morell Retires | first =Eyder | last =Peralta | website =NPR | date =2013-06-12 | access-date =2018-04-03 | archive-date =2015-04-15 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150415075751/http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2013/06/12/191061035/cia-deputy-director-michael-morell-retires | dead-url =no }}</ref>。之后于2008年到2010年担任国务院贸易事务法律助理顾问<ref name="afp">{{Cite news|last=AFP|date=2013-06-12|title=Avril Haines appointed first female CIA deputy director|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/10117458/Avril-Haines-appointed-first-female-CIA-deputy-director.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927113837/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/northamerica/usa/10117458/Avril-Haines-appointed-first-female-CIA-deputy-director.html|archive-date=2018-09-27|issn=0307-1235}}</ref>。

2010年任职于{{tsl|en|White House Counsel|白宫法律顾问}}办公室，任白宫总统国家安全事务副助理兼副法律顾问<ref>{{cite news | url =http://articles.philly.com/2013-06-13/news/39954613_1_cia-michael-morell-benghazi | title =CIA deputy director retires | first =Kimberly | last =Dozier | newspaper =The Philadelphia Inquirer | date =2013-06-13 | access-date =2013-11-29 | archive-date =2016-03-19 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160319000318/http://articles.philly.com/2013-06-13/news/39954613_1_cia-michael-morell-benghazi | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

2013年4月18日，奥巴马提名海恩斯出任{{tsl|en|Legal Adviser of the Department of State|国务院法律顾问}}，接任辞职回[[耶鲁法学院|耶鲁法学院]]任教的[[高洪株|高洪株]]<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2013/04/18/presidential-nominations-sent-senate | title =Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate | author =White House Office of the Press Secretary | publisher =whitehouse.gov | date =2013-04-18 | access-date =2013-06-22 | archive-date =2013-04-21 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20130421222000/http://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2013/04/18/presidential-nominations-sent-senate | dead-url =no }}</ref>。然而奥巴马于6月13日撤回提名，改提名她为{{tsl|en|Deputy Director of the Central Intelligence Agency|中央情报局副局长}}<ref>{{cite news | url =https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/13/us/cia-to-get-first-woman-in-no-2-job.html?_r=1& | title =C.I.A. to Get First Woman in No. 2 Job | first =Scott | last =Shane | newspaper =The New York Times | date =2013-06-12 | access-date =2017-02-26 | archive-date =2018-08-21 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180821163411/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/06/13/us/cia-to-get-first-woman-in-no-2-job.html?_r=1& | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref name="afp" />，接任时任中情局代局长{{tsl|en|Michael Morell|迈克尔·莫雷尔}}。副局长一职无须参议院确认，海恩斯遂于2013年8月9日莫雷尔离任当天即时上任<ref>{{cite news | url=https://articles.washingtonpost.com/2013-06-12/world/39918735_1_brennan-s-haines-cia-s | title=CIA's deputy director to be replaced with White House lawyer | first1=Karen | last1=DeYoung | first2=Greg | last2=Miller | work=The Washington Post | date=2013-06-12 | access-date=2017-08-24 | archive-date=2013-12-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205164754/http://articles.washingtonpost.com/2013-06-12/world/39918735_1_brennan-s-haines-cia-s | dead-url=no }}</ref>，成为首位出任该职位的女性，同时[[吉娜·哈斯佩尔|吉娜·哈斯佩尔]]成为首位获提名为中情局局长的职业女情报官员<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/DC-Decoder/2013/0613/Why-Obama-chose-woman-with-no-CIA-experience-for-No.-2-CIA-job | title=Why Obama chose woman with no CIA experience for No. 2 CIA job | first=Jennifer Skalka | last=Tulumello | work=The Christian Science Monitor | date=2013-06-13 | access-date=2013-11-29 | archive-date=2013-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131129110211/http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/DC-Decoder/2013/0613/Why-Obama-chose-woman-with-no-CIA-experience-for-No.-2-CIA-job | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/new-cia-deputy-avril-haines-hosted-erotica-readings-90s-article-1.1372072 | title=New CIA deputy Avril Haines hosted erotica readings in the '90s | first=Adam | last=Edelman | work=New York Daily News | date=2013-06-13 | access-date=2013-11-29 | archive-date=2013-12-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203124552/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/new-cia-deputy-avril-haines-hosted-erotica-readings-90s-article-1.1372072 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年，海恩斯推翻中情局检察总长的裁定，决定不处罚入侵撰写[[中情局虐囚报告|中情局虐囚报告]]参议院职员的电脑的中情局人员<ref>{{cite book | url =https://books.google.com/books?id=dGpqCgAAQBAJ&q=charlie+savage+haines+IG+cia+torture&pg=PT589 | title =Power Wars | first =Charlie | last =Savage | date =2015-11-03 | isbn =9780316286602 | access-date =2020-10-03 | archive-date =2020-11-23 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20201123175212/https://books.google.com/books?id=dGpqCgAAQBAJ&q=charlie+savage+haines+IG+cia+torture&pg=PT589 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。随后她参与项目，处理呈交参议院报告中的敏感信息<ref name="proxy">{{Cite web|last=Ackerman|first=Spencer|date=2020-07-07|title=The Proxy War Over a Top Biden Adviser|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/the-proxy-war-over-joe-biden-adviser-avril-haines?ref=scroll|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726121233/https://www.thedailybeast.com/the-proxy-war-over-joe-biden-adviser-avril-haines?ref=scroll|archive-date=2020-07-26|access-date=2020-07-16|website=The Daily Beast}}</ref>。2015年{{Citation needed|date=November 2020}}，海恩斯获提名为[[美国副国家安全顾问|副国家安全顾问]]，成为首位出任该职务的女性<ref>{{Cite web|last=Jones|first=Dustin|date=2020-11-23|title=Avril Haines Nominated As First Female Director Of National Intelligence|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/biden-transition-updates/2020/11/23/938132034/avril-haines-nominated-as-first-female-director-of-national-intelligence|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202015028/https://www.npr.org/sections/biden-transition-updates/2020/11/23/938132034/avril-haines-nominated-as-first-female-director-of-national-intelligence|archive-date=2020-12-02|access-date=2020-11-26|website=NPR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2017-11-14|title=A Top Intelligence Officer Joins the Law School|url=https://www.law.columbia.edu/news/archive/top-intelligence-officer-joins-law-school|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622231958/http://www.law.columbia.edu/news/2017/11/avril-haines-national-security|archive-date=2018-06-22|access-date=2018-12-11|website=Columbia Law School}}</ref><ref>{{cite press release|url=https://obamawhitehouse.archives.gov/the-press-office/2014/12/18/statement-president-selection-avril-haines-deputy-national-security-advi|publisher=White House|access-date=2015-01-12|date=2014-12-18|title=Statement by the President on the Selection of Avril Haines as Deputy National Security Advisor|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110032135/https://www.whitehouse.gov/the-press-office/2014/12/18/statement-president-selection-avril-haines-deputy-national-security-advi|archive-date=2016-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在奥巴马政府任职期间，海恩斯与[[约翰·歐文·布伦南|约翰·歐文·布伦南]]合作无间，共同在幕后推出[[无人航空载具|无人机]]“定点击杀目标”的行政政策<ref name="Klaidman13"/>。[[美國公民自由聯盟|美國公民自由聯盟]]抨击这项政策违反国际人权准则<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kaufman|first=Brett Max|date=2016-07-01|title=President Obama's New, Long-Promised Drone 'Transparency' Is Not Nearly Enough|url=https://www.aclu.org/blog/national-security/targeted-killing/president-obamas-new-long-promised-drone-transparency-not|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726115255/https://www.aclu.org/blog/national-security/targeted-killing/president-obamas-new-long-promised-drone-transparency-not|archive-date=2020-07-26|access-date=2020-07-16|website=ACLU}}</ref>。2016年总统竞选期间的[[2016年美国民主党全国委员会邮件泄密事件|邮件门事件]]中，身为副国家安全顾问的海恩斯召开系列会议，商讨应对黑客入侵及文件泄漏的对策<ref>{{cite web |last1=Lipton |first1=Eric |last2=Sanger |first2=David E. |last3=Shane |first3=Scott |title=The Perfect Weapon: How Russian Cyberpower Invaded the U.S. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/13/us/politics/russia-hack-election-dnc.html |website=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-12-06 |date=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2017-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170527134128/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/13/us/politics/russia-hack-election-dnc.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===私人机构===
卸下官职后，海恩斯获[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]聘任多个职位，担任哥伦比亚世界计划（Columbia World Projects）高级研究学者兼副所长，2020年5月获提名该计划的下任主任，接替{{tsl|en|Nicholas Lemann|尼古拉斯·莱曼}}。该项目负责对世界正面临的一些基本根本性挑战进行学术资助<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-11-23|title=Statement on Columbia World Projects deputy director Avril Haines' nomination by President-elect Biden as director of national intelligence|url=https://worldprojects.columbia.edu/news-media/statement-columbia-world-projects-deputy-director-avril-haines-nomination-president|access-date=2020-11-24|website=Columbia World Projects|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206164508/https://worldprojects.columbia.edu/news-media/statement-columbia-world-projects-deputy-director-avril-haines-nomination-president|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-05-26|title=Avril Haines to Serve as Next Director of Columbia World Projects|url=https://worldprojects.columbia.edu/news-media/avril-haines-serve-next-director-columbia-world-projects|access-date=2020-11-24|website=Columbia World Projects|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206164442/https://worldprojects.columbia.edu/news-media/avril-haines-serve-next-director-columbia-world-projects|dead-url=no}}</ref>。还担任[[哥伦比亚法学院|哥伦比亚法学院]]{{tsl|en|Human Rights Institute|人权研究院}}和国家安全法律计划（National Security Law Program）的研究员<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.inspire2serve.gov/commissioner/avril-haines|title=Avril Haines|website=Inspire2Serve|access-date=2019-05-04|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504192032/https://www.inspire2serve.gov/commissioner/avril-haines|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

海恩斯还是{{tsl|en|National Commission on Military, National, and Public Service|全国军事、国家与公共事务委员会}}委员<ref>{{Cite web|last=Williams|first=Chris|date=2020-11-23|title=Who is Avril Haines, Joe Biden's director of national intelligence nominee?|url=https://www.fox5atlanta.com/news/who-is-avril-haines-joe-bidens-director-of-national-intelligence-nominee|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130095136/https://www.fox5atlanta.com/news/who-is-avril-haines-joe-bidens-director-of-national-intelligence-nominee|archive-date=2020-11-30|access-date=2020-11-26|website=WAGA-TV}}</ref>、[[雪城大学|雪城大学]]安全政策与法律研究所（Institute for Security Policy and Law）的杰出研究员<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://securitypolicylaw.syr.edu/about_the_institute_for_security_policy_and_law/people/distinguished-fellows/|work=Syracuse University Institute for Security Policy and Law|title=Distinguished Fellows|access-date=2020-11-23|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126231658/https://securitypolicylaw.syr.edu/about_the_institute_for_security_policy_and_law/people/distinguished-fellows/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

另为[[Palantir_Technologies|Palantir Technologies]]提供咨询<ref name="proxy" />，是{{tsl|en|WestExec Advisors|WestExec Advisors}}的职员<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Mullins|first1=Brody|last2=Bykowicz|first2=Julie|date=2020-11-25|title=Biden Cabinet Picks Face Scrutiny Over Ties to WestExec Firm|work=The Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/biden-cabinet-picks-face-scrutiny-over-ties-to-westexec-firm-11606331281|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-11-26|issn=0099-9660|id={{ProQuest|2464196936}}|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201185604/https://www.wsj.com/articles/biden-cabinet-picks-face-scrutiny-over-ties-to-westexec-firm-11606331281}}</ref>。2020年6月末，海恩斯负责为[[喬·拜登2020年美國總統競選|乔·拜登总统竞选团队]]监督外交政策并量度国家政策，她所在的[[布鲁金斯学会|布鲁金斯学会]]的网站突然删除她履历中任职于Palantir等公司的经历<ref>{{cite news|last=Hussain|first=Murtaza|date=2020-06-26|title=Controversial Data-Mining Firm Palantir Vanishes from Biden Adviser's Biography After She Joins Campaign|website=The Intercept|url=https://theintercept.com/2020/06/26/biden-adviser-avril-haines-palantir/|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627184935/https://theintercept.com/2020/06/26/biden-adviser-avril-haines-palantir/|archive-date=2020-06-27}}</ref>。

===国家情报总监===
2020年11月23日，海恩斯获[[美国总统当选人|美国总统当选人]][[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]提名为[[國家情報總監|國家情報總監]]，成为首位出任该职务的女性<ref name="wsj-confirm-nom">{{cite news |first1=Ken |last1=Thomas |first2=Andrew |last2=Restuccia |title=Biden Reveals Some Cabinet Picks |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/biden-reveals-some-cabinet-picks-11606152632 |access-date=2020-11-23 |newspaper=The Wall Street Journal |date=2020-11-23 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123173716/https://www.wsj.com/articles/biden-reveals-some-cabinet-picks-11606152632 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web|last1=Crowley|first1=Michael|last2=Smialek|first2=Jeanna|date=2020-11-23|title=Biden Will Nominate First Woman to Lead Intelligence, Latino for Homeland Security|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/23/us/politics/biden-nominees.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123170639/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/23/us/politics/biden-nominees.html|archive-date=2020-11-23|access-date=2020-11-23|newspaper=The New York Times}}</ref>。

== 政治立场 ==
2018年，海恩斯公开支持[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]提名[[吉娜·哈斯佩尔|吉娜·哈斯佩尔]]出任中情局局长的争议性决定。尽管没有评价哈斯佩尔过往表现，她还是很欣赏哈斯佩尔对情报界的了解，这一观点在白宫对哈斯佩尔的宣传中获应和<ref name="ct20180318">{{cite news|last=Reichmann|first=Deb|date=2018-03-18|title=Trump's pick to lead CIA to face questions about torture|agency=Associated Press|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/nation-world/ct-trump-cia-director-20180313-story.html|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726211649/https://www.chicagotribune.com/nation-world/ct-trump-cia-director-20180313-story.html|archive-date=2020-07-26}}</ref><ref name="wh">{{cite web|date=2018-05-08|title=Gina Haspel Has Defended Our National Security|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/gina-haspel-defended-national-security/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508210800/https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/gina-haspel-defended-national-security/|archive-date=2018-05-08|access-date=2018-05-08|website=whitehouse.gov|publisher=White House}}</ref>。哈斯佩尔据报曾于2002年和2003年负责中情局多个秘密拷问地点的运作，而她也承认曾协助销毁记录中情局审讯者拷问过程的录像带<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kessler|first=Glenn|date=2018-05-10|title=CIA director nominee Haspel and the destruction of interrogation tapes: Contradictions and questions|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/fact-checker/wp/2018/05/11/cia-director-nominee-haspel-and-destruction-of-interrogation-tapes-contradictions-and-questions/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711183805/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/fact-checker/wp/2018/05/11/cia-director-nominee-haspel-and-destruction-of-interrogation-tapes-contradictions-and-questions/|archive-date=2018-07-11|access-date=2018-07-16|newspaper=Washington Post}}</ref>。有非营利组织领导者担心公开批评海恩斯力挺哈斯佩尔会招致“职业报复”<ref>{{Cite web|last=Kaye|first=Jeffrey|date=2020-07-08|title=Biden Advisor an "Apologist for Torture," an Architect of "Kill Lists"|url=http://accuracy.org/release/biden-advisor-an-apologist-for-torture-an-architect-of-kill-lists/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722231647/http://accuracy.org/release/biden-advisor-an-apologist-for-torture-an-architect-of-kill-lists/|archive-date=2020-07-22|access-date=2020-07-16|website=Institute for Public Accuracy}}</ref>。

